The paper deals with the analysis of MIMO systems and channels, which are typically studied in the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the impact of channel correlation and power imbalance, which are relevant to the Signal Processing (cs.SI) and Computer Engineering (cs.CE) sub-categories. Finally, the paper uses asymptotic analysis of large MIMO systems, which is a topic of interest in the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
